title: Nintendo DS Full Collection (0001-6203+All Demos+Alternative ROM
description:
Please stay and seed!!! 
 This distribution contains: 
 1. Nintendo DS original ROMs from 0001 to 6203 in "NDS" folder from http://romuniverse.com 
 2. Nintendo DS demo ROMs from x001 to x192 (strictly demo with continued edition) and from z001 to z178 (exclusive preedition, only in demo) in "NDS" folder from http://romuniverse.com 
 3. 3 BIOSes in "NDS" folder 
 4. List and Conversion Dat v3 in "From EmuMovies" folder 
 5. Nintendo DS Advanscene Snaps in "From EmuMovies" folder 
 6. Nintendo DS BOX in "From EmuMovies" folder 
 7. Nintendo DS Manuals in "From EmuMovies" folder 
 8. WinDS PRO 2013.7.0 which contains 3 emulators of Nintendo DS for Windows in "SoftwareEmulatorsfor Windows" directory 
 9. In "Tools" folder the following things: 
 a) Brain's NDS ROM Manager 
 b) DS Rom Organiser 
 c) NDSCRC 
 d) NDSTokyoTrim 
 e) Offline List (with images of Nintendo DS and other game systems from http://www.advanscene.com and other) 
 f) RomCenter 
 g) Rominator 
 h) RToolDS 
 i) ClrMAME Pro 
 and other 
 10. 124 fan translations in "Fan Translations" folder (1 to Dutch, 54 to English, 4 to French, 5 to German, 9 to Italian, 2 to Polish, 8 to Portuguese, 29 to Russian, 12 to Spanish) 
 11. Alternative Nintendo DS ROMs from http://www.emuparadise.me and from other sites in "Alternative Nintendo DS by Numbers" folder (it's ROMs presented famous releasers) 

 Also: 
 all emulators of Nintendo DS for all systems, DPG Player, DPG Converters, Homebrew. 

 P.S. Original ROMs are from http://romuniverse.com or from
 Alternative ROMs are from http://www.emuparadise.me or from http://www.dicastia.com 
 Mix ROMs are from http://www.games-engine.com or from http://www.ndsr.net or from http://romsds.net
